{"tid":103160,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[訴已投] 部iphone壞左 拎去整但唔受理","createTime":"2017-02-01T06:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T09:04:24.000Z","uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7a0ce5b318cb632912e4a9ad7777b805d383e29","tid":103160,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T06:43:40.000Z","msg":"滑雪部電話一直都壞壞地<br />\n唔知係個數據問題定點<br />\n完全收唔到電話同whsapp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但屌佢老味廣告訊息又收到<br />\n腥到whsapp出去但硬係收唔到人地whsapp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都壞左個幾月 由聖誕開始已經係咁<br />\n岩岩拎去整<br />\nApple個店員望撚左部電話一陣 然後個表情好似係似笑非笑咁同你講你部電話其實無問題<br />\n講講下仲大聲笑左出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌佢老味咩意思<br />\n我已經即時投訴左佢<br />\n<br />\n同埋我想問有咩電話維修公司介紹返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係想整返好部機姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af26e2ab63fa2611af88b9d0ef957e1b98926ff0","tid":103160,"uid":5741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T06:45:50.000Z","msg":"會唔會真係數據問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0217a45ec234c7364cc41619ac26b530e65c9201","tid":103160,"uid":28506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T06:46:39.000Z","msg":"係咪人地已讀不回你咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29217e5b9be5676ef79dabfe312b198e71f419a4","tid":103160,"uid":1996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T06:48:19.000Z","msg":"都冇人搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8caa8772037bde6d66fecd67659ceb63